# ─── INSTRUCTOR-ONLY (do NOT publish) ──────────────────────────
# Anything in this section is Bayram's pre-class playbook. Students
# get the Constitution + bot source + skills + the public Block 2
# README; they DON'T get the lesson plan, the planted-bug dossiers,
# the cohort roster, or the slide-deck source.

