instructor/

# TARS memory seeds: DENY-BY-DEFAULT. Only the Constitution (TARS's
# runtime system prompt) is public — everything else under
# memory_seeds/ may contain student data, lesson designs, instructor-
# only content, or verbatim chat quotes. New subdirs added later
# (transcripts/, personas/, etc.) inherit this default automatically.
cohort-agent/memory_seeds/*
!cohort-agent/memory_seeds/00-constitution.md

